6d09984239bf6f11aaf193f706062399be8","tid":705453,"uid":90601,"like":213,"dislike":0,"score":213,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T07:40:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180526/s00001/0ef13baa9e64fc8a19d44453ee5f6ce0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180526%2Fs00001%2F0ef13baa9e64fc8a19d44453ee5f6ce0.jpg&h=587d98df&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T01:33:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edb5cea85f360ebb1b08f854f0a4b72c7f3501ce","tid":705453,"uid":132302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a46c76a00f447eaa6a57c8745c9d6e816cec9a86","tid":705453,"uid":93251,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ce22e8f92ef775808dcc2a816b74b120775313de","tid":705453,"uid":117906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T08:40:43.000Z","msg":"禮頓大把政府project, 大把獲未爆出黎"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T01:32:46.000Z","msg":"唔知點解呢幾年禮頓靜係接到政府PROJECT呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T01:39:44.000Z","msg":"【沙中線】禮頓承辦本地大量基建工程　與UGL集團來至同一母公司 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n港鐵沙中線紅磡站月台鋼筋接駁造假事件已持續發酵約一周，但涉事的總承建商「禮頓建築（亞洲）有限公司」，至今仍未交代事件。翻查資料，禮頓過往承辦多項本地大型基建工程，包括港珠澳大橋、中環灣仔繞道，以及多個港鐵工程，不過根據過往報道指，當中部分曾發生工業意外，又爆發罷工，惹來非議。<br />\n<br />\n另外，禮頓的母公司CIMIC Group Limited，旗下子公司亦包括UGL集團，即涉嫌向前特首梁振英提供5,000萬元的澳洲公司。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/196803/%E6%B2%99%E4%B8%AD%E7%B7%9A-%E7%A6%AE%E9%A0%93%E6%89%BF%E8%BE%A6%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E5%9F%BA%E5%BB%BA%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B-%E8%88%87ugl%E9%9B%86%E5%9C%98%E4%BE%86%E8%87%B3%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%80%E6%AF%8D%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F196803%2F%25E6%25B2%2599%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25B7%259A-%25E7%25A6%25AE%25E9%25A0%2593%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2587%258F%25E5%259F%25BA%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%25A8%258B-%25E8%2588%2587ugl%25E9%259B%2586%25E5%259C%2598%25E4%25BE%2586%25E8%2587%25B3%25E5%2590%258C%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%25AF%258D%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8&d=98R5m9l%2B3%2F2o4DkYFN788ywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=fac78f07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/196803/%E6%B2%99%E4%B8%AD%E7%B7%9A-%E7%A6%AE%E9%A0%93%E6%89%BF%E8%BE%A6%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E5%9F%BA%E5%BB%BA%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B-%E8%88%87ugl%E9%9B%86%E5%9C%98%E4%BE%86%E8%87%B3%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%80%E6%AF%8D%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8</a>"},{"pid":"573133752ffb17f3b07f20f48d8cc2d0110c60c5","tid":705453,"uid":183844,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"285076d09984239bf6f11aaf193f706062399be8","tid":705453,"uid":90601,"like":213,"dislike":0,"score":213,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T07:40:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180526/s00001/0ef13baa9e64fc8a19d44453ee5f6ce0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180526%2Fs00001%2F0ef13baa9e64fc8a19d44453ee5f6ce0.jpg&h=587d98df&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T01:43:31.000Z","msg":"我信㗎 我信你哋真係廢 真係唔撚得掂 <br />\n話時話呢條死仆街又話有cancer所以唔做政府嘅 點解仲未死㗎 我信你㗎仆街仔 點解你要呃我？"},{"pid":"a19f33aa92e16be8b39ff46fb75d06cd10ba01ed","tid":705453,"uid":78473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T01:53:48.000Z","msg":"炸撚曬佢,再起過算啦"},{"pid":"92ac4512fcc6437fb63bd4eb0e7272b3338cd295","tid":705453,"uid":3858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T02:16:28.000Z","msg":"將軍澳藍田隧道 都係禮頓中建<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/f